#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:12 01e806b1b5d143fd85138c2fa2e113d3
msgid "目前可以归纳出以下 2 种搜索问题的技巧："
msgstr "Currently, the following two search techniques can be summarized:"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:14 ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:18 9f3171b933864436a3e8f01e0ed1c4d9 a09f88b550d24ec6a828211a942ca651
msgid "搜索关键词"
msgstr "Search by Keywords"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:15 ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:28 3f2c556963fe4df8add6345f8a9fc50f 4f3befab495648f58b1f2debefa5dea1
msgid "排除某个关键词"
msgstr "Exclude a Keyword"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:20 27f8dffee06345078ce80bbef411f168
msgid "将问题中的关键词提取出来并搜索它们，此时搜索结果会得到最匹配的结果。"
msgstr "Extract the keywords from the question and search for them. The search results will then show the best-matching results."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:23 fc3abe84da324fc088bdb176e2d7dabb
msgid "比如问题为：``ESP32 的 Bluetooth LE 吞吐量是多少？``"
msgstr "For example, if the question is: ``What is the Bluetooth LE throughput of ESP32?``"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:25 8cd2fa869d9442b4a6661b8310d1c19a
msgid "此时搜索：``ESP32``、``BLE`` 和 ``吞吐量`` 等关键字为宜。"
msgstr "In this case, it is recommended to search for keywords such as ``ESP32``, ``BLE``, and ``throughput``."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:30 90851360cab2488c90a3ba6edbbfa286
msgid "在搜索内容中添加一个标识符 ``-``, 格式为： ``关键词  -排除关键词``。此时搜索结果不会出现有排除关键词的结果。"
msgstr "Add the identifier ``-`` to the search content in the following format: ``keyword  -excluded_keyword``. In this case, search results containing the excluded keyword will not appear."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:32 70ff8ad39b0c4a7999c81ba5cf9c9f4d
msgid "比如搜索：``ESP32 -ble``。任何搜索结果中有 ``ble`` 的结果将会被过滤。"
msgstr "For example, search for: ``ESP32 -ble``. Any search result containing ``ble`` will be filtered out."

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:37 3470156546d94bffbfffc4ac3998c40c
msgid "在掌握上述 ``搜索问题技巧`` 后，可以利用 ESP-FAQ 已经做好的分类来提取想搜索问题里的关键词并搜索。以下是此网站的框架："
msgstr "After mastering the above ``Tips for Searching Questions``, you can use the existing categories in ESP-FAQ to extract keywords from the question you want to search for and then search for them. The following is the framework of this website:"

#: ../../source/docs/taobao/question-search.rst:40 862fa4d317654f3d91110d6c3477588f
msgid "ESP-FAQ"
msgstr "ESP-FAQ"

